00:14:48.958 --> 00:14:52.642
hot zi im ongekhapt azoy, zi hot im tse- dos ponem, hot er zi geshosn.

00:14:54.775 --> 00:14:57.654
di froy, az zi fartseylt mir, azoy veynt zi!

00:14:58.960 --> 00:15:03.307
f- m'zet es. m'zet es. ikh hob es nisht gezen.

00:15:03.786 --> 00:15:05.602
ikh bin nisht geven in Oyshvits.

00:15:08.815 --> 00:15:10.344
ir hot geredt mi-

