dos hot dos iz mir, un ikh hob oykh nisht gezen.

00:15:46.058 --> 00:15:48.161
ikh hob dos nisht gezen, Mendele.

00:15:48.555 --> 00:15:51.519
un fun di draysik yor hot er shoyn nisht genumen.

00:15:51.610 --> 00:15:53.612
