00:15:54.023 --> 00:16:01.883
un di di ale di mayne khavetorins, ale khavetorins, yunge kinder, yunge meydlekh, un froyen, meydlekh,

00:16:01.883 --> 00:16:04.811
zenen geven gut khavetorins, frantsoyzishe,

00:16:04.811 --> 00:16:08.310
oykhet genumen, un zey ge- ge- getsapt dos blut.

00:16:08.535 --> 00:16:10.621
fun zey getsapt oykhet dos blut.

00:16:12.923 --> 00:16:14.503
