00:16:20.668 --> 00:16:26.349
ir vilt nokh epes tsugebn? ir vilt nokh epes zogn?

00:16:23.348 --> 00:16:28.391
? neyn, ikh hob nisht, ikh hob dokh nisht vos.

00:16:28.701 --> 00:16:33.757
ikh hob nisht vos. dos vos di froy hot mir gezogt, dos geb ikh. dos hob ikh nisht gezen.

00:16:33.797 --> 00:16:38.178
