m'hot genumen mayn alte mame, zi iz nokh geven a yunge, zi iz nokh geven yung.

00:19:36.756 --> 00:19:40.142
mayn mame zi volt nokh gekont lebn, haynt shoyn nisht.

00:19:40.536 --> 00:19:45.271
az ikh bin tsv- tsvey un nayntsik, volt zi shoyn nisht gelebt.

00:19:45.598 --> 00:19:49.794
ober bay akht un draysik hot zi nokh gelebt, hot ikh geshikt a pekl,

00:19:50.948 --> 00:19:53.034
