00:21:40.686 --> 00:21:45.860
ikh di keyn fete zakhn tor ikh gor nisht esn. keyn fete zakhn gornisht.

00:21:45.867 --> 00:21:55.395
ober broyt, a bisele zalts, tor ikh gor nisht esn. gornisht. gornisht. gornisht gornisht.

