ikh es di burikes,

00:22:07.517 --> 00:22:15.378
un gekoyft a kilo kartofles, ikh hob genumen tsvey kartofles, ikh hob mir gemakht a bisele PUREE, on milekh, on puter,

00:22:15.378 --> 00:22:19.323
azoy tseribn, arayngegosn borsht. dos hob ikh esn.

00:22:19.718 --> 00:22:24.026
ober s'dokh on zalts. s'tsuker yo, ober s'dokh on zalts.

