00:29:26.875 --> 00:29:32.843
yo dertseylt mir vegn der fotografye, di tsveyte, dertseylt mir vegn yener fotografye.

00:29:33.473 --> 00:29:34.243
yene.

00:29:33.473 --> 00:29:35.323
fun yener?

00:29:35.548 --> 00:29:40.149
yene, ober di kinder heysn nisht Zaydnfeld, zey heysn Goldbaum.

00:29:40.763 --> 00:29:46.173
yene bin ikh m'geven oyf a khasene oyf mayn zun oyf Leon's khasene.

00:29:46.500 --> 00:29:51.050
iz geganen Leon un er hot geheysn makhn bilder azelkhene.

00:29:51.175 --> 00:29:53.565
emes? iz shoyn.

00:29:54.027 --> 00:29:56.501
vos ver shteyt do oyf dem bild?

00:29:56.946 --> 00:29:59.778
Leon, ale shteyen mir oyfn bild.

00:29:59.778 --> 00:30:09.050
Leon, di mame, un Zhak, Leon, Abe, Lazar, ale.

00:30:09.050 --> 00:30:10.811
ale shteyen mir oyfn bild.

00:30:17.331 --> 00:30:20.601
ven hot ir aroysgenumen di ershte fotografye?

00:30:20.588 --> 00:30:23.090
in tsvey tsvey un fertsikstn yor.

00:30:23.090 --> 00:30:26.921
ikh zol gebn ale kinder a foto. un,

00:30:26.918 --> 00:30:28.399
ir hot gegebn?

00:30:28.397 --> 00:30:31.047
yo, zey hobn ale mitgenumen fotos.

00:30:31.047 --> 00:30:33.694
zey hobn zey gegebn, zey hobn zey nisht tsurik gebrengt.

00:30:33.717 --> 00:30:37.761
ober mayn foto hob ikh bahaltn. dos iz mayn foto, ikh hob bahaltn.

00:30:37.851 --> 00:30:40.347
vi azoy hot ir dos bahaltn?

00:30:40.012 --> 00:30:44.446
ikh hob gegebn a goye vos ikh hob zi gekont, hot zi gehaltn di foto.

00:30:44.446 --> 00:30:49.213
di ale papirn hob ikh dokh nisht genumen, ikh veys dokh nisht ver s'hot zey genumen. di kinder hobn,

00:30:49.213 --> 00:30:52.020
Suzan hot gemuzt nemen di ale papirn.

00:30:52.212 --> 00:30:55.820
ikh hob dokh gornisht genumen, ikh hob dokh nisht gehat keyn kop tsu nemen keyn papirn.
